---
description: Checklist for API package changes in this repo. Apply whenever modifying api/v*/. Ensure validation, annotations/markers, generation, and tests are done before moving on.
globs: api/v*/**/*.go
alwaysApply: false
---

- API change checklist (MUST):
  - Review the API schema against the agreed plan:
    - ensure required resources are present,
    - remove resources that are not part of the target model.
  - Validate markers/annotations on fields:
    - required fields have no `omitempty`,
    - validation markers are present where needed.
  - Check for shared types and duplication:
    - shared types must live in `common_types.go`.
- Run code generation (MUST):
  - `bash hack/generate_code.sh` after API changes.
  - This is mandatory and blocks moving forward until done.
- Run API tests (MUST):
  - `cd api && go test ./...`.
  - Do NOT proceed until tests are green.

- Default behavior (MUST):
  - Treat codegen + API tests as automatic follow-up to any API change.
